description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the Nursing team to work on Tysul Eye Unit at Glangwili General Hospital. The Unit supports pre-assessment, ophthalmic day surgery, nurse led clinics and emergency clinics on a daily basis. We also support the AMD service in Amman Valley Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full training will be given. The service has expanded and will continue to do so to meet the service needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable, but not essential for this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Senior Sister Cerys Stacey&lt;br /&gt;01267 227828&lt;br /&gt;cerys.stacey@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
